text: The City of Inglewood is hosting a FREE COVID-19 VACCINATION site, MARCH 9 & 11, 2021. To be eligible you must be 65 years of age or older. Must bring (1) Proof of Identity/Age and (2) Proof of  Insurance, if you have health insurance. #inglewood #vaccine #COVID19 #seniors https://t.co/6G8dkThbpS
